  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00308', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設社會上僅有A與B二人，其對某一公共財的個人需求函數分別為P =100-Q 與P =200-2Q， A A B B 其中P為價格，Q為數量。若提供公共財的邊際成本為$60，在公共財配置效率下，下列敘述何者 正確？', '["A與B二人分別消費20與40單位的公共財", "A與B二人分別消費40與20單位的公共財", "A與B二人的願付價格分別為20與40元", "A與B二人的願付價格分別為40與20元"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00309', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據寇斯定理（CoaseTheorem），外部性問題發生的主要原因為：', '["外部性的種類很多", "外部性的規模很大", "受外部性影響的對象並不確定", "自願性協商的外部性市場並不存在 12060"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00310', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '皮寇克（A.T.Peacock）與魏斯曼（J.Wiseman）認為公共支出因社會發生重大干擾因素而增加， 即為：', '["干擾效果（interferenceeffect）", "結構轉變（structuralbreaks）效果", "集中效果（concentrationeffect）", "位移效果（displacementeffect）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00311', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '公共支出計畫評估，下列何種情況下市場價格是衡量社會生產財貨成本的良好指標？', '["完全競爭市場", "政府課稅", "非充分就業", "政府補貼"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00312', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '公共支出計畫已訂有明確的目標，依成本有效性分析（cost-effectivenessanalysis），在眾多達成目 標的方案中，要求的條件是：', '["淨利益現值最大", "執行成本最低", "社會貼現率最低", "內部報酬率最高"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00313', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '政府提供更多的社會住宅，使租屋者的「消費者剩餘」增加。所謂「消費者剩餘」是指租屋者：', '["願意支付的租金總和，超過他們實際支付的租金總和", "願意支付的租金總和，遠低於他們實際支付的租金總和", "需支付更高的租金", "可租到的房屋更少"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('promotion-6f0ba476-moex-00314', 'promotion-6f0ba476', 'promotion-6f0ba476-moex-110-f6c431ec', 'sub-promotion-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '兩消費者對一公共財 Q（該財貨之單位價格為40）之需求函數均是P=l00-0.5Q，則兩人協商之 林達爾（E.Lindahl）均衡：', '["公共財數量為120", "公共財數量為60", "公共財數量為160", "公共財數量為80"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:28:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd589c3d00", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7631fcb9fa89", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110170", "c": "118", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員升官等考試、110年關務人員升官等考試、110年交通事業公路人員升資考試、110年交通事業港務人員升資考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "promotion", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
